   * ./configure.in: BeOS, liba52 and chroma plugin compilation fixes.
   * ./plugins/dvd/dvd_access.c: removed a warning.
   * ./src/misc/configuration.c: Solaris fixes by Meuuh.
   * ./FAQ: removed outdated stuff.

