  . patched 2 debian bugs
     (see http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/pkgreport.cgi?pkg=vlc)
  . improved the snapshot generation

2001-02-04 Sunday 03:06  sam

  . removed obsolete video_yuv_mmx.S
